graphs":["<em>Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.</em>","Viper Home is an impressive contender in the saturated market of <a href=\"/best-diy-home-security\">DIY home security systems</a>. This alarm system contains everything you need to secure your home in a convenient start-up package. In addition, the Viper Home system boasts a smart design and, according to most users, consistent and reliable performance.","The starter kit of this system comes with a smart control hub, a motion detector and a sensor that can be placed on a door or window. Like most DIY security systems, this one allows you to purchase additional devices a la carte, including cameras and sirens. This gives you the flexibility to expand the system on an as-needed basis. Keep in mind that if you use a camera, you have to pay a monthly fee if you want to take advantage of the system’s live video feed.","An appealing feature of the Viper system is you can broaden its functionality to include home automation and vehicle security. This means you can use the system to secure your home and automate lighting and thermostats in addition to securing your home – all through the convenient Viper app.","Consistent performance is a vital aspect of any DIY home alarm and if online reviews are any indication, Viper Home doesn’t disappoint in this regard. The system has earned a solid reputation for its reliability, sending notifications whenever a security event occurs while the system is armed. Its motion sensor also has an effective range of nearly 40 feet.","Aside from its touted reliability, users of this do-it-yourself alarm system also praise its modern yet unobtrusive design. When it comes to a wireless alarm system, you want devices that are inconspicuous and easily blend in with the surroundings. The components of Viper Home do just that and enable you to place them nearly anywhere in your home without calling attention to them.","Expandability, effectiveness and convenience are all hallmarks of top-notch DIY home alarms, and it seems as though the Viper Home excels in each of these areas. The system also enables you to control and monitor your home security system from a mobile app."]},"id":"129d98c9-6ea4-4993-90a9-56516f038350","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58901","url":"/viper-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-02-24T20:28:02Z","datePublished":"2014-02-24T20:28:02Z","name":"Viper Home","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-02-24T20:28:02Z","id":"qnpYn7EBhywDE3TRXZ5NAC","meta":{"title":"Viper Home Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Viper Home security start-up kit is a great DIY solution. But does it offer the protection you are looking for? Read our review to find out the details."},"products":[{"slug":"viper-home","url":"/product/viper-home","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T18:38:32Z","name":"Viper Home","dateModified":"2019-04-16T18:38:32Z","id":"YWj6ojwRHWjmpULo4GY39Z","dateImported":"2019-04-16T16:01:12